title: 2013 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 43)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2013 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Here is what I think the genre break down might look like for this bundle...  METAL/HARDCORE: Acera, All Became New, August Burns Red, Battleship, Color Me Valiant, Dissimulator, Enfield, The Flesh Of The Kings, Letter To The Exiles, My Ransomed Soul, Oh Redeemer.  ROCK: Anberlin, Matt Price.  CONTEMPORARY: Anthem Lights, Robbie Seay Band.  GOSPEL: Blind Boys Of Alabama, The Collingsworth Family, The Greenes, Jay Parrack And Vocal Event, Lamar Campbell And Spirit Of Praise, Oslo Gospel Choir, Tony Gore.  PRAISE & WORSHIP: Common Call, Pete Reynolds, Victory Worship.  ALTERNATIVE: Dustin Smith, Greg Cooper, The Letter Black, Michael Payton, Over The Ocean.  HIP-HOP/RAP: Fly Geara, Heath McNease, Rell Riley, Vita Christi.  SINGER-SONGWRITER: Michael Gallaugher.  R&B: Michelle Williams

Bundle 43 includes the following 43 releases.  Our year to date total shared is now up to 1,216 titles...
